{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "c2615926-e1f9-4836-a902-7491185f0115", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c2615926-e1f9-4836-a902-7491185f0115@1.pkg/1772597624933/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597625717", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c2615926-e1f9-4836-a902-7491185f0115@1.pkg/1772597624933/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597625717"}, "identifier": "c2615926-e1f9-4836-a902-7491185f0115", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>本题考查坚持国家利益至上的相关知识。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>A: 题文中&ldquo;狼牙山五壮士&rdquo;为了国家而不惜牺牲自己，说明为了国家利益，有时不仅要放弃个人利益，甚至要献出自己的生命，故A正确</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>C: 为了国家利益而英勇献身的精神在任何时期都需要，故B错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>B：国家利益和个人利益在根本上是一致的，维护国家利益不一定会损害公民的个人利益。D: 维护国家利益的不仅是军人，其他公民也能做到。故D错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>9.1认识总体国家安全观</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编） 抗日战争时期，在狼牙山抗击日军的战斗中，八路军五位战士临危不惧，英勇阻击。面对敌人，他们宁死不屈，义无反顾地纵身跳下数十丈深的悬崖，被称为&ldquo;狼牙山五壮士&rdquo;。由此可见（ &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编） 抗日战争时期，在狼牙山抗击日军的战斗中，八路军五位战士临危不惧，英勇阻击。面对敌人，他们宁死不屈，义无反顾地纵身跳下数十丈深的悬崖，被称为“狼牙山五壮士”。由此可见（  ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c2615926-e1f9-4836-a902-7491185f0115@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755140043129", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>为了国家利益，有时甚至要献出自己生命</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>维护国家利益必定要牺牲公民的个人利益</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>和平发展时期不再需要这种英勇献身的精神</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>只有成为军人，才能真正做好维护国家利益</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编） 抗日战争时期，在狼牙山抗击日军的战斗中，八路军五位战士临危不惧，英勇阻击。面对敌人，他们宁死不屈，义无反顾地纵身跳下数十丈深的悬崖，被称为&ldquo;狼牙山五壮士&rdquo;。由此可见（ &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44be